Weeks et al., Respondents, v. Lowenberger, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. May 6, 1889.)

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Allen and Bookstaver, JJ.

O. L. Cohen, for appellant. S. S. Harris, for respondents.

Judgment affirmed, with costs. (Memorandum on papers.)
